Description: README
        =======
        
        Extra third party extensions for ``Python-Markdown``
        
        Install
        --------
        
        ```bash
          $ pip install md_ext
        ```
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        ```python
        
        import markdown
        
        data = "![alt](image.png){width=600}"
        md = markdown.Markdown(extensions=['md_ext.img'])
        html = md.convert(data)
        print(html)
        ```
        
        Output:
        
        ```python
        '<p><img src="image.png" width="600" /></p>'
        ```
        
